00042 MTKt_status MtkFileGridFieldToDimList(
00043   const char *filename, 
00044   const char *gridname, 
00045   const char *fieldname,
00046   int *dimcnt,          
00047   char **dimlist[],     
00048   int **dimsize          )
00049 {
00050   MTKt_status status;       /* Return status. */
00051   MTKt_status status_code;      /* Return status of this function. */
00052   intn hdfstatus;               /* HDF-EOS return status */
00053   int32 Fid = FAIL;             /* HDF-EOS File ID */
00054 
00055   if (filename == NULL)
00056     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_NULLPTR);
00057 
00058   /* Open HDF file for reading */
00059   hdfstatus = Fid = GDopen((char*)filename,DFACC_READ);
00060   if (hdfstatus == FAIL)
00061     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDFEOS_GDOPEN_FAILED);
00062 
00063   /* Read dimension list. */
00064   status = MtkFileGridFieldToDimListFid(Fid, gridname, fieldname, 
00065                     dimcnt, dimlist, dimsize);
00066   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);
00067   
00068   /* Close HDF file. */
00069   GDclose(Fid);
00070   
00071   return MTK_SUCCESS;
00072 
00073 ERROR_HANDLE:
00074   GDclose(Fid);
00075 
00076   return status_code;

00084 MTKt_status MtkFileGridFieldToDimListFid(

00131   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);

00144     
00145   temp = strtok(list,",");
00146   i = 0;

00150     (strncmp(temp, "XDim", sizeof(*temp))) != 0 &&
00151     (strncmp(temp, "YDim", sizeof(*temp))) != 0) {
00152       (*dimlist)[i] = (char*)malloc((strlen(temp) + 1) * sizeof(char));
00153       if ((*dimlist)[i] == NULL)
00154     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_MALLOC_FAILED);
00155       strcpy((*dimlist)[i],temp);
00156       ++i;
00157     }

00162   *dimcnt = i;
00163 
00164   if (*dimcnt > 0) {
00165 
00166     /* Get dimension size info */
00167     for (i = 0; i < *dimcnt; ++i) {

00169     }
00170 
00171     /* Resize lists to account for removing dimensions */
00172     *dimlist = (char **)realloc((void *)*dimlist, *dimcnt * sizeof(char*));
00173     if (*dimlist == NULL)
00174       MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_REALLOC_FAILED);
00175     *dimsize = (int *)realloc((void *)*dimsize, *dimcnt * sizeof(int));
00176     if (*dimsize == NULL)
00177       MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_REALLOC_FAILED);
00178   } else {
00179     MtkStringListFree(*dimcnt, dimlist);
00180     free(*dimsize);
00181     *dimsize = NULL;
00182   }
00183 
00184   free(basefield);
00185   free(extradims);
00186   free(list);
00187   GDdetach(Gid);
00188 
00189   return MTK_SUCCESS;
00190 
00191 ERROR_HANDLE:
00192   if (dimlist != NULL && *dimlist != NULL)
00193     MtkStringListFree(*dimcnt, dimlist);
00194 
00195   if (dimsize != NULL)
00196     {
00197       free(*dimsize);
00198       *dimsize = NULL;
00199     }
00200 
00201   if (dimcnt != NULL)
00202     *dimcnt = -1;
00203 
00204   if (basefield != NULL) free(basefield);
00205   if (extradims != NULL) free(extradims);
